Title: Lorentz and CPT violations in QED

controversiesComments: 7 pages, LaTex file, 2 references added

We rediscuss the recent controversy on a possible Chern-Simons like termgenerated through radiative corrections in QED with a CPT violating term. Weemphasize the fact that any absence of an {\sl a priori} divergence should beprediction can be made on the corresponding quantity.